transArray.content: Although the room is small, the environment is good and the waiters are very friendly.

Simple love lasts the longest, companionship in the ordinary is the most reassuring, people who understand you are the warmest, we work hard to be the people who understand you best, my little master’s praise warms people’s hearts more than the sun in winter, no matter the wind or rain, Orange Beijing Our friends at Wukesong Hotel are always waiting for you. Although our rooms are not big, they are well-equipped. We always insist on using our attentiveness to exchange for your peace of mind when you stay. If you like it, remember to come often ~ I wish you a great time Have a prosperous year and everything goes well!
